.TH "nvme_init_get_log_media_unit_stat" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_media_unit_stat" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_media_unit_stat \- Initialize passthru command for Media Unit Status
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_media_unit_stat
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u16 domid "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_media_unit_stat_log *mus "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "domid" 12
Domain Identifier selection, if supported
.IP "mus" 12
User address to store the Media Unit statistics log
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_MEDIA_UNIT_STATUS
